text: Denis Savenkov (born 17 September 1983) is a Belarusian gymnast. He competed at the 2004 Summer Olympics and the 2008 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Belarus Category:Gymnasts at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 2008 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Gomel
